{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846430232,"sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","part":{"id":"prt_d78b211c7001ZK3LIxx27cHQfm","messageID":"msg_d78b204d400134LHYF6MBnA9lD","sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_2900857117d845f58b90b47d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: <!-- TODO: 设计目的 -->\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 Package Layout\n10: \n11: ```\n12: pkg/agentd/\n13: ├── idle_cleanup.go        — TODO\n14: ├── idle_cleanup_test.go   — TODO\n15: └── ...\n16: ```\n17: \n18: ### 1.3 Data Flow\n19: \n20: <!-- TODO: 数据流图 -->\n21: \n22: ### 1.4 Dependencies\n23: \n24: <!-- TODO: 依赖表 -->\n25: \n26: ---\n27: \n28: ## 2. Data Structures\n29: \n30: <!-- TODO: 数据结构定义 -->\n31: \n32: ---\n33: \n34: ## 3. API Contracts\n35: \n36: <!-- TODO: API 契约 -->\n37: \n38: ---\n39: \n40: ## 4. Core Implementation\n41: \n42: <!-- TODO: 核心实现要点 -->\n43: \n44: ---\n45: \n46: ## 5. Error Handling\n47: \n48: <!-- TODO: 错误处理策略 -->\n49: \n50: ---\n51: \n52: ## 6. Testing Strategy\n53: \n54: <!-- TODO: 测试策略 -->\n55: \n56: ---\n57: \n58: ## 7. Deployment Considerations\n59: \n60: <!-- TODO: 部署考量 -->\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## 8. Implementation Steps\n65: \n66: <!-- TODO: 分步实现计划 -->\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## 9. Future Changes\n71: \n72: <!-- TODO: 未来可能的变更 -->\n\n(End of file - total 72 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\n<!-- TODO: 设计目的 -->\n\n### 1.2 Package Layout\n\n```\npkg/agentd/\n├── idle_cleanup.go        — TODO\n├── idle_cleanup_test.go   — TODO\n└── ...\n```\n\n### 1.3 Data Flow\n\n<!-- TODO: 数据流图 -->","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md","time":{"start":1775846430222,"end":1775846430231}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846431449,"sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","part":{"id":"prt_d78b2168b001Vu1RC5W5jP1Vqf","messageID":"msg_d78b204d400134LHYF6MBnA9lD","sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_faa64ac5d2cb47fda425199a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/agentd\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube 实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，基于 controller-runtime 构建 Sandbox 资源的空闲清理控制器。当 Sandbox 的 `last-activity-time` 注解标识的最后活动时间超过 15 分钟（`SessionExpirationTimeout`）时，控制器自动删除该 Sandbox，释放集群资源。\n10: \n11: 当前沙箱的空闲清理逻辑由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 通过轮询 Store（Redis）实现，存在以下局限：\n12: - 依赖外部 Store，Store 不可用时清理失效\n13: - 轮询间隔（默认 5 分钟）导致清理延迟\n14: - 无法利用 Kubernetes 原生 watch 机制实时响应 Sandbox 状态变化\n15: \n16: `agentd` 作为独立的 in-cluster 控制器，直接 watch Sandbox CR 的创建/更新事件，通过 requeue 机制在精确的过期时间点触发删除，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲清理能力。\n17: \n18: ## 范围\n19: \n20: ### 包含\n21: \n22: 1. **Reconciler 实现**\n23:    - `Reconciler` 结构体：嵌入 `client.Client`，持有 `*runtime.Scheme`\n24:    - `Reconcile(ctx, req)` 方法：实现 Sandbox 空闲检测与删除的核心逻辑\n25:    - 从 Sandbox 注解 `last-activity-time`（`workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`）读取最后活动时间\n26:    - 解析 RFC3339 格式时间戳，计算 `expirationTime = lastActivity + SessionExpirationTimeout`\n27:    - 过期时调用 `Delete`，未过期时 `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`\n28: \n29: 2. **SetupWithManager**\n30:    - 注册 Sandbox 资源的 controller-runtime watch\n31:    - 使用 `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)` 模式\n32: \n33: 3. **Binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`**\n34:    - Scheme 注册：core Kubernetes 类型 + `sandboxv1alpha1`（`sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`）\n35:    - 构造 controller-runtime Manager：禁用 metrics 服务（`BindAddress: \"0\"`），禁用 health probe（`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`）\n36:    - 注册 Reconciler 并启动 Manager，监听 `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` 实现优雅关闭\n37: \n38: 4. **常量定义**\n39:    - `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`：空闲过期阈值\n40: \n41: 5. **单元测试**\n42:    - Sandbox 不存在时返回空结果（NotFound 处理）\n43:    - 缺少 `last-activity-time` 注解时不删除、不 requeue\n44:    - 注解值非 RFC3339 格式时返回错误 + 30s requeue\n45:    - 未过期时返回正确 `RequeueAfter`\n46:    - 已过期时触发 Delete 调用\n47:    - Delete 返回 NotFound 时视为成功\n48: \n49: ### 不包含\n50: \n51: - TTL（最大存活时间）清理：由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 负责\n52: - 孤儿 CR 清理：由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 负责\n53: - Store（Redis）交互：agentd 不依赖 Store，仅读取 Sandbox CR 注解\n54: - Sandbox 创建/更新逻辑：由 WorkloadManager 负责\n55: - 自定义闲置阈值：固定使用 `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15min`，不从 CR Spec 读取\n56: - Metrics / Health Probe：本控制器禁用这些端点（S 级简化）\n57: \n58: ## 架构概要\n59: \n60: ### 组件关系\n61: \n62: ```\n63: Kubernetes API Server\n64:     │\n65:     ├── watch Sandbox CR (agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1)\n66:     │       │\n67:     │       ▼\n68:     │   agentd Reconciler\n69:     │       │\n70:     │       ├── 读取 annotation: last-activity-time\n71:     │       ├── 计算: expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n72:     │       ├── 未过期 → RequeueAfter(time.Until(expirationTime))\n73:     │       └── 已过期 → Delete(Sandbox)\n74:     │\n75:     └── WorkloadManager LifecycleManager（独立运行，负责 TTL/孤儿清理）\n76:             │\n77:             └── 轮询 Redis Store → 清理过期沙箱\n78: ```\n79: \n80: ### 目录结构\n81: \n82: ```\n83: cmd/agentd/\n84: └── main.go           — Binary 入口：Scheme 注册、Manager 构造、启动\n85: pkg/agentd/\n86: ├── reconciler.go     — Reconciler 结构体 + Reconcile 方法\n87: ├── reconciler_test.go — 单元测试\n88: └── const.go          — SessionExpirationTimeout 常量\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ### Reconcile 算法\n92: \n93: ```\n94: 1. Get Sandbox by req.NamespacedName\n95: 2. If NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n96: 3. If other error → return (Result{}, err)\n97: 4. Read annotation \"last-activity-time\"\n98: 5. If missing or empty → return (Result{}, nil)\n99: 6. Parse as RFC3339\n100:    - If parse error → return (Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)\n101: 7. expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n102: 8. If now.After(expirationTime):\n103:      Delete(sandbox)\n104:      - If NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n105:      - If error → return (Result{}, err)\n106:      - Else → return (Result{}, nil)\n107: 9. Else:\n108:      return (Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n109: ```\n110: \n111: ## 影响分析\n112: \n113: ### 直接影响\n114: \n115: | 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n116: |------|------|------|\n117: | `cmd/agentd/main.go` | 新增 | Binary 入口 |\n118: | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | 新增 | Reconciler 实现 |\n119: | `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` | 新增 | 单元测试 |\n120: | `pkg/agentd/const.go` | 新增 | 常量定义 |\n121: | `go.mod` | 修改 | 新增 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`、`sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` 依赖 |\n122: \n123: ### 上游依赖（本变更依赖的已完成组件）\n124: \n125: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n126: |------|----------|\n127: | `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | controller-runtime 框架（Manager、Reconciler 模式） |\n128: | `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Sandbox CRD 类型定义 |\n129: | `pkg/workloadmanager` | 仅引用 `LastActivityAnnotationKey` 常量 |\n130: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | errors.IsNotFound、runtime.Scheme 等 |\n131: \n132: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n133: \n134: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n135: |------|----------|\n136: | 集群运维 | 可部署 agentd Deployment 实现原生 K8s 空闲清理 |\n137: | WorkloadManager | 可与 LifecycleManager 共存，形成双层清理保障 |\n138: \n139: ### 无影响的组件\n140: \n141: - `pkg/router/` — 仅写入 `last-activity-time` 注解，不依赖 agentd\n142: - `pkg/workloadmanager/` — 独立运行，清理逻辑不受 agentd 影响\n143: - `pkg/apis/` — CRD 类型定义独立\n144: - `client-go/` — 生成代码不涉及 agentd\n145: - `pkg/picod/` — 沙箱内守护进程，不感知清理控制器\n146: \n147: ### 风险评估\n148: \n149: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n150: |------|------|----------|\n151: | controller-runtime 依赖引入增加构建体积 | 低 | 仅 agentd binary 受影响，其他组件不变 |\n152: | 与 LifecycleManager 重复删除 | 低 | Delete 是幂等操作，API Server 返回 NotFound 时双方均视为成功 |\n153: | 注解格式异常导致 reconcile 错误 | 低 | 解析错误返回 30s requeue，不会阻塞其他 Sandbox |\n154: | 大量 Sandbox 同时过期导致 API Server 压力 | 低 | controller-runtime 的 workqueue 有速率限制；S 级规模场景可控 |\n155: | agentd 未部署时清理回退到 LifecycleManager | 无风险 | LifecycleManager 始终运行，agentd 为增强而非替代 |\n156: \n157: ### 与现有组件的交互\n158: \n159: | 组件 | 交互方式 | 影响 |\n160: |------|----------|------|\n161: | Router | 在代理请求时更新 Sandbox 的 `last-activity-time` 注解 | 无影响。Router 不感知 agentd 存在 |\n162: | WorkloadManager | 创建 Sandbox 时设置 `last-activity-time` 注解 | 无影响。WorkloadManager 已有此逻辑 |\n163: | LifecycleManager | 独立轮询 Store 清理过期沙箱 | 互补关系：agentd 基于 K8s watch，LifecycleManager 基于 Store 轮询 |\n164: \n165: ## 备选方案\n166: \n167: ### 1. 独立 controller-runtime 控制器（✅ 选定方案）\n168: \n169: **做法**：新建 `pkg/agentd` 包，使用 controller-runtime 框架 watch Sandbox CR，基于 `last-activity-time` 注解触发删除。\n170: \n171: **优点**：\n172: - 利用 K8s 原生 watch 机制，无需轮询，延迟低\n173: - 不依赖外部 Store（Redis），减少故障面\n174: - controller-runtime 提供成熟的 workqueue、重试、leader election 等基础设施\n175: - 与 LifecycleManager 形成双层保障，互不干扰\n176: \n177: **缺点**：\n178: - 引入 controller-runtime 依赖，增加构建体积\n179: - 需要独立部署 agentd Deployment\n180: \n181: **决策**：采用。符合 Kubernetes Operator 最佳实践，变更范围可控（S 级），与现有架构互补。\n182: \n183: ### 2. 扩展 LifecycleManager 增加 watch 模式\n184: \n185: **做法**：在现有 `LifecycleManager` 中添加 informer watch，替代轮询逻辑。\n186: \n187: **优点**：无需新增 binary，复用现有部署  \n188: **缺点**：LifecycleManager 职责膨胀（当前负责 TTL/孤儿/幽灵清理 + Store 交互），混合 watch 和轮询两种模式增加复杂度；改动范围超出 S 级  \n189: **决策**：不采用。单一职责原则，watch 模式更适合独立控制器。\n190: \n191: ### 3. Kubernetes TTL Controller（`ttlSecondsAfterFinished`）\n192: \n193: **做法**：利用 K8s 原生 TTL 机制，在 Sandbox 上设置 `ttlSecondsAfterFinished`。\n194: \n195: **优点**：无需自定义控制器，K8s 原生支持  \n196: **缺点**：TTL 从资源创建/完成时间开始计算，无法基于\"最后活动时间\"动态更新；不满足空闲检测需求  \n197: **决策**：不采用。业务需求是基于活动时间的空闲检测，非固定 TTL。\n198: \n199: ### 4. CronJob 定期清理\n200: \n201: **做法**：部署 CronJob 定期扫描 Sandbox 注解并删除过期资源。\n202: \n203: **优点**：实现简单，无需常驻进程  \n204: **缺点**：清理延迟取决于 CronJob 周期；无法实现精确的过期时间点触发；扫描全量 Sandbox 效率低  \n205: **决策**：不采用。watch 模式更高效、延迟更低。\n206: \n207: ## 实现要点\n208: \n209: 1. **常量定义**：`SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`，与 LifecycleManager 的 `DefaultIdleTimeout` 保持一致\n210: 2. **注解引用**：使用 `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`（值为 `\"last-activity-time\"`），避免魔法字符串\n211: 3. **时间解析**：严格使用 `time.RFC3339` 格式，解析失败返回错误 + 30s requeue\n212: 4. **Delete 幂等**：`errors.IsNotFound(err)` 时视为成功，返回 `(Result{}, nil)`\n213: 5. **Requeue 精度**：未过期时 `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`，确保在过期时刻精确触发\n214: 6. **Scheme 注册**：`sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder)` + `scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder)`（core 类型）\n215: 7. **Manager 配置**：禁用 metrics 和 health probe（`BindAddress: \"0\"`），最小化资源占用\n216: \n217: ## 验收标准\n218: \n219: 1. **Reconciler 行为**\n220:    - [ ] Sandbox 不存在时返回 `(Result{}, nil)`\n221:    - [ ] 缺少 `last-activity-time` 注解时不删除、不 requeue\n222:    - [ ] 注解为空字符串时不删除、不 requeue\n223:    - [ ] 注解值非 RFC3339 格式时返回错误 + `RequeueAfter: 30s`\n224:    - [ ] 未过期时返回 `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`\n225:    - [ ] 已过期时调用 `Delete` 删除 Sandbox\n226:    - [ ] Delete 返回 NotFound 时视为成功\n227: \n228: 2. **Manager 配置**\n229:    - [ ] Scheme 包含 core 类型和 `sandboxv1alpha1`\n230:    - [ ] Metrics 服务禁用（`BindAddress: \"0\"`）\n231:    - [ ] Health Probe 禁用（`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`）\n232:    - [ ] 信号处理实现优雅关闭\n233: \n234: 3. **测试覆盖**\n235:    - [ ] `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` 全部通过\n236:    - [ ] 使用 fake client 模拟所有 reconcile 分支\n237:    - [ ] 覆盖 Get NotFound、注解缺失、解析错误、未过期、已过期、Delete NotFound 场景\n238: \n239: 4. **代码质量**\n240:    - [ ] `go vet ./pkg/agentd/...` 无告警\n241:    - [ ] `go mod tidy` 后无未使用依赖\n242: \n243: ## 状态\n244: \n245: - [ ] 提案审查\n246: - [ ] 实现\n247: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 247 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n**Module:** pkg/agentd\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube 实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，基于 controller-runtime 构建 Sandbox 资源的空闲清理控制器。当 Sandbox 的 `last-activity-time` 注解标识的最后活动时间超过 15 分钟（`SessionExpirationTimeout`）时，控制器自动删除该 Sandbox，释放集群资源。\n\n当前沙箱的空闲清理逻辑由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 通过轮询 Store（Redis）实现，存在以下局限：\n- 依赖外部 Store，Store 不可用时清理失效\n- 轮询间隔（默认 5 分钟）导致清理延迟\n- 无法利用 Kubernetes 原生 watch 机制实时响应 Sandbox 状态变化\n\n`agentd` 作为独立的 in-cluster 控制器，直接 watch Sandbox CR 的创建/更新事件，通过 requeue 机制在精确的过期时间点触发删除，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲清理能力。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775846431439,"end":1775846431447}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846432676,"sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","part":{"id":"prt_d78b21b4d001TJ71s6ptXnHVW7","messageID":"msg_d78b204d400134LHYF6MBnA9lD","sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d2c2da30edb84adb94ed137d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `pkg/agentd`, `cmd/agentd`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** S\n8: - **Base specs:** `idle-cleanup/spec.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: Reconciler watches Sandbox CR\n13: \n14: The system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API group `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`. The reconciler SHALL be triggered on Sandbox create and update events via `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)`.\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Sandbox creation triggers reconcile\n17: \n18: - **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n19: - **WHEN** a new `Sandbox` object is created in the cluster\n20: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object's namespace and name\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: Sandbox update triggers reconcile\n23: \n24: - **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n25: - **WHEN** an existing `Sandbox` object is updated (including annotation changes)\n26: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object's namespace and name\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: Sandbox deletion triggers reconcile\n29: \n30: - **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n31: - **WHEN** a `Sandbox` object is deleted from the cluster\n32: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked and returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` without error\n33: \n34: ### Requirement: Reconciler data structures\n35: \n36: The system SHALL define the following types in `pkg/agentd`:\n37: \n38: ```go\n39: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n40: \n41: type Reconciler struct {\n42:     client.Client\n43:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n44: }\n45: ```\n46: \n47: `SessionExpirationTimeout` SHALL be the fixed idle expiration threshold. The `Reconciler` struct SHALL embed `client.Client` for API server operations and hold a `*runtime.Scheme` for type registration.\n48: \n49: #### Scenario: SessionExpirationTimeout is 15 minutes\n50: \n51: - **GIVEN** the `pkg/agentd` package is imported\n52: - **WHEN** `SessionExpirationTimeout` is read\n53: - **THEN** its value equals `15 * time.Minute`\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: Reconciler embeds client.Client\n56: \n57: - **GIVEN** a `Reconciler` instance is constructed\n58: - **WHEN** the instance is used\n59: - **THEN** it can call `Get`, `Delete`, and other `client.Client` methods directly\n60: \n61: ### Requirement: Get Sandbox and handle not found\n62: \n63: The `Reconcile` method SHALL retrieve the `Sandbox` object using `r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`. When the API server returns `NotFound`, the reconciler SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` without error.\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: Sandbox no longer exists\n66: \n67: - **GIVEN** a reconcile request for namespace `\"default\"`, name `\"sandbox-abc\"`\n68: - **WHEN** `r.Get` returns `errors.IsNotFound(err)`\n69: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n70: \n71: #### Scenario: API server error on Get\n72: \n73: - **GIVEN** a reconcile request for a valid Sandbox\n74: - **WHEN** `r.Get` returns a non-NotFound error (e.g., connection refused)\n75: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, err)` to trigger retry\n76: \n77: ### Requirement: Idle detection via annotation\n78: \n79: The system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the Sandbox metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` without delete action or requeue.\n80: \n81: The constant `LastActivityAnnotationKey` SHALL be defined in `pkg/workloadmanager` with value `\"last-activity-time\"`.\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Annotation is missing\n84: \n85: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with no `last-activity-time` annotation\n86: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n87: - **THEN** the reconciler returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` and the Sandbox is not deleted\n88: \n89: #### Scenario: Annotation is empty string\n90: \n91: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with `last-activity-time: \"\"`\n92: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n93: - **THEN** the reconciler returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` and the Sandbox is not deleted\n94: \n95: ### Requirement: Timestamp parsing\n96: \n97: When the `last-activity-time` annotation is non-empty, the system SHALL parse it with `time.RFC3339`. On parse error, the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err)`.\n98: \n99: #### Scenario: Valid RFC3339 timestamp\n100: \n101: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is `\"2026-04-10T10:00:00Z\"`\n102: - **WHEN** `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, ...)` is called\n103: - **THEN** parsing succeeds and returns the corresponding `time.Time` value\n104: \n105: #### Scenario: Invalid timestamp format\n106: \n107: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is `\"not-a-timestamp\"`\n108: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n109: - **THEN** the reconciler returns `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)` where `err` is the parse error\n110: \n111: #### Scenario: Partial RFC3339 timestamp\n112: \n113: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is `\"2026-04-10\"`\n114: - **WHEN** `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, ...)` is called\n115: - **THEN** parsing fails and reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`\n116: \n117: ### Requirement: Expiration threshold and delete\n118: \n119: The system SHALL compute `expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`. When `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`, the system SHALL call `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)` to remove the Sandbox resource.\n120: \n121: #### Scenario: Sandbox idle beyond 15 minutes\n122: \n123: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z` and current time is `2026-04-10T10:16:00Z`\n124: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n125: - **THEN** `expirationTime` is `2026-04-10T10:15:00Z`, `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` is true, and `r.Delete` is called\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: Sandbox not yet expired\n128: \n129: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z` and current time is `2026-04-10T10:05:00Z`\n130: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n131: - **THEN** `expirationTime` is `2026-04-10T10:15:00Z`, `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` is false, and no delete occurs\n132: \n133: #### Scenario: Exactly at expiration boundary\n134: \n135: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z` and current time is `2026-04-10T10:15:00Z`\n136: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n137: - **THEN** `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` is false (equal, not after), and result is `RequeueAfter` with a small positive duration or zero\n138: \n139: ### Requirement: Requeue until expiration\n140: \n141: When the Sandbox is not yet expired, the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)` to schedule the next reconciliation at the exact expiration time.\n142: \n143: #### Scenario: RequeueAfter is positive duration\n144: \n145: - **GIVEN** `expirationTime` is 10 minutes in the future\n146: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n147: - **THEN** the result is `ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: ~10m}` and `Requeue` is false\n148: \n149: #### Scenario: RequeueAfter approaches zero near expiration\n150: \n151: - **GIVEN** `expirationTime` is 1 second in the future\n152: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n153: - **THEN** the result is `ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: ~1s}`\n154: \n155: ### Requirement: Delete idempotency\n156: \n157: When `r.Delete` returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL treat it as success and return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`. Other delete errors SHALL be returned as `(ctrl.Result{}, err)` to trigger retry.\n158: \n159: #### Scenario: Sandbox already deleted by another controller\n160: \n161: - **GIVEN** the LifecycleManager deleted the Sandbox between reconcile Get and Delete\n162: - **WHEN** `r.Delete` returns `errors.IsNotFound(err)`\n163: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n164: \n165: #### Scenario: Delete fails with transient error\n166: \n167: - **GIVEN** the API server returns a connection error on Delete\n168: - **WHEN** `r.Delete` is called\n169: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, err)` to trigger retry\n170: \n171: ### Requirement: Successful delete result\n172: \n173: When `r.Delete` succeeds (returns nil error), the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`.\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: Delete succeeds\n176: \n177: - **GIVEN** the Sandbox exists and is expired\n178: - **WHEN** `r.Delete` returns nil\n179: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n180: \n181: ### Requirement: SetupWithManager\n182: \n183: The system SHALL provide a `SetupWithManager` method on `Reconciler` that registers the controller with the manager:\n184: \n185: ```go\n186: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n187:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n188:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n189:         Complete(r)\n190: }\n191: ```\n192: \n193: #### Scenario: Controller is registered\n194: \n195: - **GIVEN** a valid `ctrl.Manager`\n196: - **WHEN** `r.SetupWithManager(mgr)` is called\n197: - **THEN** the function returns `nil` and the controller is registered to watch Sandbox resources\n198: \n199: ### Requirement: Binary entry point — Scheme registration\n200: \n201: The `cmd/agentd/main.go` SHALL construct a scheme containing core Kubernetes types and `sandboxv1alpha1` from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`:\n202: \n203: ```go\n204: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n205: \n206: func init() {\n207:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n208:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n209: }\n210: ```\n211: \n212: #### Scenario: Scheme contains core and Sandbox types\n213: \n214: - **GIVEN** the `init` function has run\n215: - **WHEN** `schemeBuilder` is inspected\n216: - **THEN** it recognizes both core `v1.Pod` and `sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox` types\n217: \n218: ### Requirement: Binary entry point — Manager configuration\n219: \n220: The binary SHALL construct a controller-runtime Manager with the following options:\n221: \n222: ```go\n223: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n224:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n225:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n226:     HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n227: })\n228: ```\n229: \n230: Metrics server SHALL be disabled (`BindAddress: \"0\"`). Health probe server SHALL be disabled (`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`).\n231: \n232: #### Scenario: Manager starts without metrics or health endpoints\n233: \n234: - **GIVEN** a valid kubeconfig is available\n235: - **WHEN** `ctrl.NewManager` is called with the specified options\n236: - **THEN** no metrics or health probe HTTP servers are started\n237: \n238: #### Scenario: Invalid kubeconfig fails fast\n239: \n240: - **GIVEN** no valid kubeconfig is available\n241: - **WHEN** `ctrl.GetConfigOrDie()` is called\n242: - **THEN** the process exits with a non-zero status\n243: \n244: ### Requirement: Binary entry point — Controller registration and startup\n245: \n246: The binary SHALL register the reconciler and start the manager:\n247: \n248: ```go\n249: if err := (&agentd.Reconciler{\n250:     Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n251:     Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n252: }).SetupWithManager(mgr); err != nil {\n253:     // exit with error\n254: }\n255: \n256: if err := mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()); err != nil {\n257:     // exit with error\n258: }\n259: ```\n260: \n261: #### Scenario: Signal-driven graceful shutdown\n262: \n263: - **GIVEN** the manager is running\n264: - **WHEN** SIGTERM or SIGINT is received\n265: - **THEN** `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` triggers graceful shutdown and `mgr.Start` returns\n266: \n267: ### Requirement: Package layout\n268: \n269: The system SHALL organize code as follows:\n270: \n271: ```\n272: cmd/agentd/\n273: └── main.go              — Binary entry point\n274: pkg/agentd/\n275: ├── reconciler.go        — Reconciler struct, Reconcile, SetupWithManager\n276: ├── reconciler_test.go   — Unit tests\n277: └── const.go             — SessionExpirationTimeout constant\n278: ```\n279: \n280: #### Scenario: Package compiles\n281: \n282: - **GIVEN** all files are in place\n283: - **WHEN** `go build ./cmd/agentd/` is run\n284: - **THEN** the build succeeds and produces an `agentd` binary\n285: \n286: #### Scenario: Package tests pass\n287: \n288: - **GIVEN** all test cases are implemented\n289: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` is run\n290: - **THEN** all tests pass with exit code 0\n291: \n292: ### Requirement: Reconcile algorithm completeness\n293: \n294: The `Reconcile` method SHALL implement the following algorithm exactly:\n295: \n296: 1. `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`\n297: 2. If `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n298: 3. If other get error → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n299: 4. `lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`\n300: 5. If `!exists || lastActivityStr == \"\"` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n301: 6. `lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`\n302: 7. If parse error → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err`\n303: 8. `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n304: 9. If `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`:\n305:    - `err := r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`\n306:    - If err and not `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n307:    - `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n308: 10. Else → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n309: \n310: #### Scenario: Full happy path — expired sandbox deleted\n311: \n312: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with `last-activity-time` set to 20 minutes ago\n313: - **WHEN** `Reconcile` is called\n314: - **THEN** steps 1-9 execute, `Delete` is called, and `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` is returned\n315: \n316: #### Scenario: Full happy path — not yet expired requeues\n317: \n318: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with `last-activity-time` set to 5 minutes ago\n319: - **WHEN** `Reconcile` is called\n320: - **THEN** steps 1-8 and 10 execute, returning `RequeueAfter: ~10m`\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: Missing annotation short-circuits\n323: \n324: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox without `last-activity-time`\n325: - **WHEN** `Reconcile` is called\n326: - **THEN** steps 1-5 execute, returning `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` at step 5\n327: \n328: ### Requirement: Code quality gates\n329: \n330: The codebase SHALL pass the following checks after implementation:\n331: \n332: - `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` produces no warnings\n333: - `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` passes all tests\n334: - `go mod tidy` results in no changes\n335: \n336: #### Scenario: go vet clean\n337: \n338: - **GIVEN** AR-018 is implemented\n339: - **WHEN** `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` is run\n340: - **THEN** no warnings or errors are reported\n341: \n342: #### Scenario: All tests pass\n343: \n344: - **GIVEN** AR-018 is implemented\n345: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` is run\n346: - **THEN** all tests pass with exit code 0\n347: \n348: #### Scenario: No unused dependencies\n349: \n350: - **GIVEN** AR-018 is implemented\n351: - **WHEN** `go mod tidy` is run\n352: - **THEN** `go.mod` and `go.sum` are unchanged\n\n(End of file - total 352 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/agentd`, `cmd/agentd`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** S\n- **Base specs:** `idle-cleanup/spec.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Reconciler watches Sandbox CR\n\nThe system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API group `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`. The reconciler SHALL be triggered on Sandbox create and update events via `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)`.\n\n#### Scenario: Sandbox creation triggers reconcile\n\n- **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n- **WHEN** a new `Sandbox` object is created in the cluster\n- **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object's namespace and name","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775846432668,"end":1775846432674}}}}
