{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846438141,"sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","part":{"id":"prt_d78b23147001fwBXuv56ncbwKA","messageID":"msg_d78b21ff9001NbAtQ4qbZ3dppk","sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_a96ad0e7e1d04b66a981949d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package handler\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"time\"\n5: \n6: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n7: )\n8: \n9: var (\n10: \tAgentRuntimeGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n11: \t\tGroup:    \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n12: \t\tVersion:  \"v1alpha1\",\n13: \t\tResource: \"agentruntimes\",\n14: \t}\n15: \tCodeInterpreterGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n16: \t\tGroup:    \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n17: \t\tVersion:  \"v1alpha1\",\n18: \t\tResource: \"codeinterpreters\",\n19: \t}\n20: \tSandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n21: \t\tGroup:    \"agents.x-k8s.io\",\n22: \t\tVersion:  \"v1alpha1\",\n23: \t\tResource: \"sandboxes\",\n24: \t}\n25: \tSandboxClaimGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n26: \t\tGroup:    \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\",\n27: \t\tVersion:  \"v1alpha1\",\n28: \t\tResource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n29: \t}\n30: )\n31: \n32: const (\n33: \tAgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n34: \tCodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n35: \tSandboxesKind       = \"Sandbox\"\n36: \tSandboxClaimsKind   = \"SandboxClaim\"\n37: )\n38: \n39: const (\n40: \tLabelManagedBy      = \"app.kubernetes.io/managed-by\"\n41: \tLabelManagedByValue = \"agentcube-workload-manager\"\n42: \tLabelSessionID      = \"runtime.agentcube.io/session-id\"\n43: \tLabelWorkloadName   = \"runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name\"\n44: \tLabelSandboxName    = \"runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name\"\n45: )\n46: \n47: const (\n48: \tAnnotationIdleTimeout    = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\n49: \tAnnotationSandboxPodName = \"agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name\"\n50: )\n51: \n52: const (\n53: \tIdentitySecretName        = \"picod-router-identity\"\n54: \tPublicKeyDataKey          = \"public.pem\"\n55: \tDefaultSandboxTTL         = 8\n56: \tDefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15\n57: )\n58: \n59: const (\n60: \tDefaultIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n61: \tMaxOrphanScanLimit = 100\n62: )\n63: \n64: const (\n65: \tGRCleanupReasonTTLExpired = \"ttl_expired\"\n66: \tGRCleanupReasonIdle       = \"idle\"\n67: \tGRCleanupReasonOrphanCR   = \"orphan_cr\"\n68: \tGRCleanupReasonGhostEntry = \"ghost_entry\"\n69: )\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package handler\n\nimport (\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n)\n\nvar (\n\tAgentRuntimeGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n\t\tGroup:    \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n\t\tVersion:  \"v1alpha1\",\n\t\tResource: \"agentruntimes\",\n\t}\n\tCodeInterpreterGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n\t\tGroup:    \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n\t\tVersion:  \"v1alpha1\",\n\t\tResource: \"codeinterpreters\",\n\t}\n\tSandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go","time":{"start":1775846438134,"end":1775846438140}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846439166,"sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","part":{"id":"prt_d78b23565001Px2KhhzFM6TIrH","messageID":"msg_d78b21ff9001NbAtQ4qbZ3dppk","sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_05d7df3a309f479dad49d07c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n8: \n9: ### Time threshold\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n13: ```\n14: \n15: Idle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n16: \n17: ### Annotation key\n18: \n19: The reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n20: \n21: - Import: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n22: - Key: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` = **`\"last-activity-time\"`**\n23: \n24: (Workload manager also sets `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` on Sandbox metadata for template-driven idle configuration; **agentd** only reads `last-activity-time`.)\n25: \n26: ### Reconciler\n27: \n28: ```go\n29: package agentd\n30: \n31: type Reconciler struct {\n32:     client.Client\n33:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n34: }\n35: \n36: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\n37: ```\n38: \n39: **Algorithm (exact behavior):**\n40: \n41: 1. `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`.\n42: 2. If `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`.\n43: 3. If other get error → return `ctrl.Result{}, err`.\n44: 4. `lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`.\n45: 5. If `exists && lastActivityStr != \"\"`:\n46:    - `lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`\n47:    - If parse err → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err`\n48:    - `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n49:    - If `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`:\n50:      - `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`; if err and not `IsNotFound` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n51:    - Else:\n52:      - `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n53: 6. `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n54: \n55: ### SetupWithManager\n56: \n57: ```go\n58: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n59:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n60:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n61:         Complete(r)\n62: }\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ## Binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n66: \n67: ### Scheme registration\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n71: \n72: func init() {\n73:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n74:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n75: }\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ### Controller-runtime manager\n79: \n80: ```go\n81: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n82:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n83:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n84:     HealthProbeBindAddress:   \"0\",\n85: })\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### Controller registration (duplicate of SetupWithManager pattern)\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n92:     For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n93:     Complete(&agentd.Reconciler{\n94:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n95:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n96:     })\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ### Run\n100: \n101: ```go\n102: mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())\n103: ```\n104: \n105: ## Watched resources\n106: \n107: | API group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n108: |-----------|---------|------|---------|\n109: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Default `For()` watch — creates, updates, deletes (per controller-runtime) |\n110: \n111: No explicit `Owns` or `Watches` — single primary resource `Sandbox`.\n112: \n113: ## Related workload-manager constants (context)\n114: \n115: From `pkg/workloadmanager` (not used by agentd reconcile logic but set when sandboxes are created):\n116: \n117: - `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"` — duration string on Sandbox CR.\n118: - `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` — **read by agentd** for idle cleanup.\n119: \n120: ## Dependencies\n121: \n122: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n123: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n124: - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`\n125: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`\n126: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` (annotation key only)\n\n(End of file - total 126 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n\n### Time threshold\n\n```go\nvar SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n```\n\nIdle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n\n### Annotation key\n\nThe reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md","time":{"start":1775846439158,"end":1775846439164}}}}
