{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846596949,"sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","part":{"id":"prt_d78b28b1100196oe1nyZwdIe4y","messageID":"msg_d78b27a58001LB1W0WqSNfBxX3","sessionID":"ses_287510ae9ffeOG04UnYpli5Vao","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_79584b6a78d246a0b11411f6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\n实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，作为基于 controller-runtime 的 Kubernetes 控制器，负责 watch `Sandbox` CR（`agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`）并根据 `last-activity-time` 注解自动清理空闲沙箱。与 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager`（基于 Redis Store 轮询）形成双层清理保障，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲检测能力。\n\n### 1.2 Package Layout\n\n```\ncmd/agentd/\n└── main.go              — Binary 入口：Scheme 注册、Manager 构造、启动\npkg/agentd/\n├── reconciler.go        — Reconciler 结构体 + Reconcile + SetupWithManager\n├── reconciler_test.go   — 单元测试（fake client）\n└── const.go             — SessionExpirationTimeout 常量\npkg/workloadmanager/\n└── const.go             — LastActivityAnnotationKey 常量（新增）\n```\n\n### 1.3 Data Flow\n\n```\nKubernetes API Server\n    │\n    ├── Sandbox Create/Update/Delete Event\n    │       │\n    │       ▼\n    │   controller-runtime Informer (cache)\n    │       │\n    │       ▼\n    │   Reconciler.Reconcile(ctx, req)\n    │       │\n    │       ├── 1. Get Sandbox by NamespacedName\n    │       │       ├── NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n    │       │       └── Error  → return (Result{}, err)\n    │       │\n    │       ├── 2. Read annotation \"last-activity-time\"\n    │       │       └── Missing/empty → return (Result{}, nil)\n    │       │\n    │       ├── 3. Parse RFC3339 timestamp\n    │       │       └── Parse error → return (Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)\n    │       │\n    │       ├── 4. Compute expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n    │       │\n    │       └── 5. Check expiration\n    │               ├── now.After(expirationTime)\n    │               │       ├── Delete(sandbox)\n    │               │       │       ├── NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n    │               │       │       ├── Error    → return (Result{}, err)\n    │               │       │       └── Success  → return (Result{}, nil)\n    │               │\n    │               └── !now.After(expirationTime)\n    │                       └── return (Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n    │\n    └── WorkloadManager LifecycleManager（独立运行，负责 TTL/孤儿/幽灵清理）\n```\n\n### 1.4 Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose | Type |\n|---|---|---|\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | Manager、Reconciler 模式、workqueue | Direct |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Sandbox CRD 类型定义 | Direct |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` | `errors.IsNotFound` 判断 | Direct |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | Scheme 注册 | Direct |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime` | `utilruntime.Must` 安全初始化 | Direct |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` | `LastActivityAnnotationKey` 常量引用 | Internal |\n\n## 2. Data Structures\n\n### 2.1 Constants\n\n```go\n// pkg/agentd/const.go\npackage agentd\n\nimport \"time\"\n\n// SessionExpirationTimeout is the fixed idle expiration threshold.\n// A Sandbox is considered expired when its last activity time plus\n// this duration has elapsed.\nvar SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n```\n\n```go\n// pkg/workloadmanager/const.go (new file)\npackage workloadmanager\n\n// LastActivityAnnotationKey is the annotation key used to store the\n// last activity timestamp on Sandbox objects. The value is an RFC3339\n// formatted timestamp updated by the Router on each proxied request.\nconst LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n```\n\n### 2.2 Reconciler\n\n```go\n// pkg/agentd/reconciler.go\npackage agentd\n\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\"\n)\n\n// Reconciler implements the idle cleanup controller for Sandbox resources.\n// It embeds client.Client for API server operations and holds a Scheme\n// for type registration.\ntype Reconciler struct {\n    client.Client\n    Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n}\n```\n\n### 2.3 Sentinel Errors\n\n无自定义 sentinel errors。所有错误来源于：\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors.IsNotFound(err)` — 资源不存在\n- `time.Parse` 返回的解析错误 — 时间戳格式非法\n- controller-runtime 返回的网络/API 错误 — 重试由框架处理\n\n### 2.4 Key Constants Reference\n\n| Constant | Value | Defined In | Used By |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `SessionExpirationTimeout` | `15 * time.Minute` | `pkg/agentd/const.go` | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` |\n| `LastActivityAnnotationKey` | `\"last-activity-time\"` | `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`, `pkg/router/`, `pkg/workloadmanager/` |\n\n## 3. API Contracts\n\n本控制器不暴露 HTTP API。与 Kubernetes API Server 的交互通过 controller-runtime client 完成。\n\n### 3.1 Watched Resources\n\n| API Group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Create, Update, Delete（controller-runtime `For()` 默认行为） |\n\n### 3.2 Reconcile Contract\n\n**Input:** `ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request`\n\n**Output:** `(ctrl.Result, error)`\n\n| Condition | Result | Error | Side Effect |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Sandbox NotFound | `{}` | `nil` | None |\n| Get error (non-NotFound) | `{}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n| Annotation missing/empty | `{}` | `nil` | None |\n| Timestamp parse error | `{RequeueAfter: 30s}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n| Not expired | `{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}` | `nil` | None |\n| Expired, Delete NotFound | `{}` | `nil` | None (already deleted) |\n| Expired, Delete error | `{}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n| Expired, Delete success | `{}` | `nil` | Sandbox deleted |\n\n### 3.3 Manager Configuration\n\n| Option | Value | Rationale |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Scheme` | core + `sandboxv1alpha1` | 支持 Sandbox 类型操作 |\n| `Metrics.BindAddress` | `\"0\"` | S 级简化，禁用 metrics 服务 |\n| `HealthProbeBindAddress` | `\"0\"` | S 级简化，禁用 health probe |\n| Signal handler | `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` | SIGTERM/SIGINT 优雅关闭 |\n\n## 4. Core Implementation\n\n### 4.1 Reconcile Method\n\n```go\nfunc (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n    sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}\n    if err := r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox); err != nil {\n        if errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n            return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n        }\n        return ctrl.Result{}, err\n    }\n\n    lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n    if !exists || lastActivityStr == \"\" {\n        return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n    }\n\n    lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)\n    if err != nil {\n        return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err\n    }\n\n    expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n\n    if time.Now().After(expirationTime) {\n        if err := r.Delete(ctx, sandbox); err != nil && !errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n            return ctrl.Result{}, err\n        }\n        return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n    }\n\n    return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil\n}\n```\n\n### 4.2 SetupWithManager\n\n```go\nfunc (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n    return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n        For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n        Complete(r)\n}\n```\n\n### 4.3 Binary Entry Point\n\n```go\n// cmd/agentd/main.go\npackage main\n\nimport (\n    \"flag\"\n    \"os\"\n\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n    utilruntime \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime\"\n    sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/log/zap\"\n    metricsserver \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/metrics/server\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd\"\n)\n\nvar schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n\nfunc init() {\n    utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n    utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n}\n\nfunc main() {\n    opts := zap.Options{\n        Development: true,\n    }\n    opts.BindFlags(flag.CommandLine)\n    flag.Parse()\n\n    ctrl.SetLogger(zap.New(zap.UseFlagOptions(&opts)))\n\n    mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n        Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n        Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n        HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n    })\n    if err != nil {\n        setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to start manager\")\n        os.Exit(1)\n    }\n\n    if err := (&agentd.Reconciler{\n        Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n        Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n    }).SetupWithManager(mgr); err != nil {\n        setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to create controller\", \"controller\", \"Sandbox\")\n        os.Exit(1)\n    }\n\n    setupLog.Info(\"starting manager\")\n    if err := mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()); err != nil {\n        setupLog.Error(err, \"problem running manager\")\n        os.Exit(1)\n    }\n}\n\nvar setupLog = ctrl.Log.WithName(\"setup\")\n```\n\n### 4.4 Reconcile Decision Tree\n\n```\nReconcile(ctx, req)\n├── Get(req.NamespacedName)\n│   ├── NotFound → return ({}, nil)          [已删除，无需处理]\n│   └── Error    → return ({}, err)           [API 错误，重试]\n│\n├── Annotations[LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n│   ├── Missing   → return ({}, nil)          [无活动时间，跳过]\n│   └── Empty     → return ({}, nil)          [空值，跳过]\n│\n├── time.Parse(RFC3339, value)\n│   └── Error → return ({RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)  [格式异常，30s 后重试]\n│\n├── expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n│\n└── time.Now().After(expirationTime)\n    ├── true (expired)\n    │   └── Delete(sandbox)\n    │       ├── NotFound → return ({}, nil)   [已被其他控制器删除]\n    │       ├── Error    → return ({}, err)    [删除失败，重试]\n    │       └── Success  → return ({}, nil)    [删除成功]\n    │\n    └── false (not expired)\n        └── return ({RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n```\n\n### 4.5 Time Precision Considerations\n\n- `time.Until(expirationTime)` 返回 `time.Duration`，在过期时刻临近时趋近于 0\n- controller-runtime 对 `RequeueAfter: 0` 的处理等同于立即 requeue，不会导致 busy loop\n- 当 `time.Now()` 恰好等于 `expirationTime` 时，`After()` 返回 `false`，下一次 requeue 会在下一个调度周期触发\n\n## 5. Error Handling\n\n### 5.1 Error Classification\n\n| Error Source | Error Type | Handling Strategy |\n|---|---|---|\n| `r.Get` — NotFound | `apierrors.IsNotFound` | 静默返回 `({}, nil)`，不重试 |\n| `r.Get` — 其他 | Network/API error | 返回 `({}, err)`，controller-runtime workqueue 指数退避重试 |\n| `time.Parse` | Format error | 返回 `({RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`，固定 30s 后重试 |\n| `r.Delete` — NotFound | `apierrors.IsNotFound` | 静默返回 `({}, nil)`，幂等处理 |\n| `r.Delete` — 其他 | Network/API error | 返回 `({}, err)`，controller-runtime workqueue 指数退避重试 |\n\n### 5.2 Idempotency Guarantees\n\n- **Delete 幂等**：多次调用 `Delete` 对同一 Sandbox 不会产生副作用，`IsNotFound` 视为成功\n- **Reconcile 幂等**：同一 Sandbox 的多次 reconcile 调用不会产生重复删除\n- **与 LifecycleManager 共存**：两者可能同时尝试删除同一 Sandbox，`IsNotFound` 处理确保双方均正常完成\n\n### 5.3 Error Propagation\n\n- 解析错误（`time.Parse`）返回给 controller-runtime，记录到日志但不会导致控制器崩溃\n- API 错误由 controller-runtime 的 workqueue 管理重试，自动指数退避\n- 不会 panic，所有错误路径都有明确的返回值\n\n## 6. Testing Strategy\n\n### 6.1 Unit Test Matrix\n\n| Test Case | Sandbox Exists | Annotation | Timestamp | Time vs Expiration | Expected Result |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound` | No (Get NotFound) | — | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n| `TestReconcile_GetError` | No (Get error) | — | — | — | `Result{}`, `err` |\n| `TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing` | Yes | Missing | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n| `TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty` | Yes | `\"\"` | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n| `TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp` | Yes | `\"not-a-timestamp\"` | Parse fails | — | `Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}`, `err` |\n| `TestReconcile_NotExpired` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | 5 min ago | `now < expiration` | `Result{RequeueAfter: ~10m}`, `nil` |\n| `TestReconcile_Expired` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | Delete called, `Result{}`, `nil` |\n| `TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound` | Yes (Delete NotFound) | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n| `TestReconcile_DeleteError` | Yes (Delete error) | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | `Result{}`, `err` |\n| `TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | Exactly 15 min ago | `now == expiration` | `Result{RequeueAfter: >=0}`, `nil` |\n\n### 6.2 Test Helpers\n\n```go\n// 使用 controller-runtime fake client\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"testing\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/stretchr/testify/assert\"\n    \"github.com/stretchr/testify/require\"\n    sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n    metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/types\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client/fake\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager\"\n)\n\nfunc newTestScheme() *runtime.Scheme {\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    _ = sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)\n    return scheme\n}\n\nfunc newFakeReconciler(objects ...runtime.Object) *agentd.Reconciler {\n    return &agentd.Reconciler{\n        Client: fake.NewClientBuilder().\n            WithScheme(newTestScheme()).\n            WithRuntimeObjects(objects...).\n            Build(),\n        Scheme: newTestScheme(),\n    }\n}\n\nfunc newSandbox(ns, name string, annotations map[string]string) *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox {\n    return &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Namespace:   ns,\n            Name:        name,\n            Annotations: annotations,\n        },\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 6.3 Mock Strategy\n\n- **Fake Client**：使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client/fake` 模拟 Kubernetes API Server\n- **时间控制**：测试中通过构造不同的 `last-activity-time` 值和依赖 `time.Now()` 的相对计算来覆盖过期/未过期分支\n- **Error Injection**：fake client 不支持直接注入 Get/Delete 错误，可通过自定义 `client.Client` wrapper 或使用 `WithStatusSubresource` 等 builder 选项模拟\n\n### 6.4 Test File Structure\n\n```go\n// pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go\n\nfunc TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_GetError(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_NotExpired(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_Expired(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_DeleteError(t *testing.T) { ... }\nfunc TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary(t *testing.T) { ... }\n\nfunc TestSetupWithManager(t *testing.T) { ... }\n```\n\n### 6.5 Gate Requirements\n\n- `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` — 无告警\n- `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` — 全部通过\n- `go mod tidy` — 无变更\n\n## 7. Deployment Considerations\n\n### 7.1 Deployment Manifest\n\nagentd 作为独立的 Deployment 部署在集群中：\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: agentd\n  namespace: agentcube-system\nspec:\n  replicas: 1\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: agentd\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: agentd\n    spec:\n      serviceAccountName: agentd\n      containers:\n      - name: agentd\n        image: agentcube/agentd:latest\n        resources:\n          requests:\n            cpu: 50m\n            memory: 64Mi\n          limits:\n            cpu: 200m\n            memory: 128Mi\n---\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: agentd\n  namespace: agentcube-system\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRole\nmetadata:\n  name: agentd\nrules:\n- apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n  resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n  verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n---\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: agentd\nroleRef:\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n  kind: ClusterRole\n  name: agentd\nsubjects:\n- kind: ServiceAccount\n  name: agentd\n  namespace: agentcube-system\n```\n\n### 7.2 RBAC Requirements\n\n| API Group | Resource | Verbs | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get`, `list`, `watch` | 读取 Sandbox 状态和注解 |\n| `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `delete` | 删除过期 Sandbox |\n\n### 7.3 Resource Requirements\n\n| Resource | Request | Limit | Rationale |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| CPU | 50m | 200m | 控制器轻量，仅在事件触发时工作 |\n| Memory | 64Mi | 128Mi | controller-runtime informer cache 占用 |\n\n### 7.4 Coexistence with LifecycleManager\n\n| Aspect | agentd | LifecycleManager |\n|---|---|---|\n| Trigger | K8s watch (event-driven) | Polling Redis Store (5min interval) |\n| Data Source | Sandbox CR annotations | Redis Store entries |\n| Cleanup Scope | Idle only (15min) | TTL + Idle + Orphan + Ghost |\n| Delete Idempotency | `IsNotFound` → success | `IsNotFound` → success |\n| Failure Mode | Falls back to LifecycleManager | Falls back to agentd |\n\n两者互补运行，互不依赖，Delete 操作天然幂等。\n\n## 8. Implementation Steps\n\n### Phase 1: 常量定义\n\n- [ ] 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go`，定义 `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n- [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/const.go`，定义 `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n\n### Phase 2: Reconciler 实现\n\n- [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`\n- [ ] 实现 `Reconciler` 结构体（嵌入 `client.Client` + `*runtime.Scheme`）\n- [ ] 实现 `Reconcile` 方法（完整算法）\n- [ ] 实现 `SetupWithManager` 方法\n\n### Phase 3: Binary Entry Point\n\n- [ ] 创建 `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n- [ ] Scheme 注册（core + `sandboxv1alpha1`）\n- [ ] Manager 构造（禁用 metrics/health probe）\n- [ ] Reconciler 注册 + Start\n\n### Phase 4: 单元测试\n\n- [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go`\n- [ ] 实现所有测试用例（见 6.1 测试矩阵）\n- [ ] 验证 `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` 全部通过\n\n### Phase 5: 代码质量门禁\n\n- [ ] `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` 无告警\n- [ ] `go mod tidy` 无变更\n- [ ] 验收标准对照检查（见 proposal.md 验收标准）\n\n## 9. Future Changes\n\n- **可配置过期阈值**：当前固定 15 分钟，未来可从 ConfigMap 或 Sandbox annotation 读取自定义阈值\n- **Metrics 集成**：启用 metrics 服务，暴露 `agentd_sandboxes_cleaned_total`、`agentd_reconcile_duration_seconds` 等指标\n- **Leader Election**：多副本部署时启用 controller-runtime leader election，避免重复删除\n- **Grace Period**：删除前添加宽限期，允许 Sandbox 内进程完成清理\n- **Event Recording**：删除 Sandbox 时记录 Kubernetes Event，便于审计和调试\n- **Finalizer 支持**：在删除前执行自定义清理逻辑（如清理关联的 ConfigMap/Secret）\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go\">\nERROR [78:24] cannot use (func() literal) (value of type func()) as func(interface{}) value in argument to runtime.HandleCrash\nERROR [83:24] cannot use (func() literal) (value of type func()) as func(interface{}) value in argument to runtime.HandleCrash\nERROR [88:24] cannot use (func() literal) (value of type func()) as func(interface{}) value in argument to runtime.HandleCrash\nERROR [97:24] cannot use (func() literal) (value of type func()) as func(interface{}) value in argument to runtime.HandleCrash\nERROR [102:24] cannot use (func() literal) (value of type func()) as func(interface{}) value in argument to runtime.HandleCrash\nERROR [107:24] cannot use (func() literal) (value of type func()) as func(interface{}) value in argument to runtime.HandleCrash\nERROR [116:25] cannot use (func() literal) (value of type func()) as func(interface{}) value